<div type="definition">
<p>AUTHOR whose WORK is to WRITE POEMS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. There is no common and current word for a poet, but note the occasional use of the term 詩人 "author of songs" and of gǔ 瞽 "blind singer".</p>
        </div>
